      "title": "Good news for Laf users",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The price of Laf cooking gas will be further reduced next month, said Vakapitiya, Chairman of Laf Group.",
        "He mentioned that the price of Lough gas was reduced by Rs 1050 last week and the price will be reduced by the same amount next month.",
        "The current price of a 12.5 kg Lough gas cylinder is Rs 5,800, a 5 kg cylinder is Rs 2,320 and a 2.5 kg gas cylinder is Rs 928. (a)"
      ],
